Eskom has announced that Stage 4 loadshedding will continue to be implemented until 16:00 on Thursday. Thereafter, Stage 5 loadshedding will be implemented from 16:00 on Thursday until 05:00 on Saturday. Stage 4 loadsshedding will then be implemented from 05:00 on Friday until 05:00 on Saturday, whereafter it will be reduced to Stage 3 until 16:00 on Saturday. Stage 4 will again be implemented from 16:00 on Saturday until 05:00 on Sunday. A further update will be published as soon as any significant changes occur, Eskom said.